cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is about improving the Transformer translation model for natural language processing tasks, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also introduces a new context encoder, which involves machine learning techniques (cs.AI) and deep learning models (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of parallel corpora, which is relevant to neural machine translation (cs.NE). Finally, the paper may also be relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) as it deals with the processing of textual data.
